## 11. Dependency Graph

```
app/layout.tsx
  └─ components/auth-provider.tsx ── lib/supabase-browser.ts ── @supabase/supabase-js

app/(app)/layout.tsx
  ├─ components/top-nav.tsx ── components/auth-provider.tsx
  ├─ components/floating-assistant.tsx
  └─ components/auth-gate.tsx ── components/auth-provider.tsx

app/(app)/page.tsx, meeting/[id], recording/[id], speakers, calendar, templates, settings
  ├─ lib/api-client.ts ── lib/supabase-browser.ts
  └─ components/* (cards, panels, insight/summary, mind-map)

app/api/transcribe/route.ts
  ├─ lib/supabase.ts ── @supabase/supabase-js
  ├─ lib/email.ts (scaffolding, imported)
  ├─ lib/calendar.ts (scaffolding, imported)
  └─ lib/speakers.ts (scaffolding, imported)

app/api/meetings, meeting/[id], speakers, calendar, templates
  └─ lib/supabase.ts (getUserFromRequest, supabaseAdmin)

app/api/summary, insights, mindmap, search
  └─ lib/fakeData.ts

app/home/page.tsx
  └─ components/marketing/* ── framer-motion, lucide-react

extension/recording.js ── extension/background.js ── POST /api/transcribe
extension/popup.js ── chrome.storage.local (token)

next.config.mjs ── next-pwa
```

External runtime deps: `next@16`, `react@19`, `@supabase/supabase-js`,
`framer-motion`, `lucide-react`, `next-pwa`, `@vercel/analytics`, Tailwind v4,
`class-variance-authority`, `clsx`, `tailwind-merge`.

